{"tid":1652400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[撐起雨傘]有冇人記得呢首歌","createTime":"2019-10-13T16:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T16:24:40.000Z","uid":172499,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d75534996f14225137011d32f0f2ab0206364c47","tid":1652400,"uid":172499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"所有為我城命運付出，不計個人前提我失的年輕人，<br />\n所有令香港變得更美麗的人，你們並不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C_23GElzJFo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC_23GElzJFo&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=eca23b9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C_23GElzJFo</a><br />\n靜坐人海 你我非不怕<br />\n會畏懼這樣下去怎辦<br />\n但是人生 到了這一晚<br />\n更怕未表白內心呼喊<br />\n<br />\n站在前方 勇氣驅不散<br />\n卻信越怕命運更黯淡<br />\n但是誰想 要看穿荒誕<br />\n卻會在催淚下睜開眼<br />\n<br />\n一起舉傘 一起的撐<br />\n一起儘管不安卻不孤單 對嗎<br />\n一起舉傘 舉起手撐<br />\n一起為應得的放膽爭取 怕嗎<br />\n任暴雨下 志向未倒下<br />\n雨傘是一朵朵的花<br />\n不枯也不散<br />\n<br />\n為著明天 要記得今晚<br />\n你我用鎮定面對憂患<br />\n若是人生 錯過這一晚 <br />\n怕再沒機會任意呼喊"},{"pid":"53b51fb1796f8c43b79ba5ebc6b12dcc30335825","tid":1652400,"uid":153341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfec487c3669f7a1b6b3ded5605deb2321b024b9","tid":1652400,"uid":248674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:17:42.000Z","msg":"一起舉傘 一起的撐<br />\n一起儘管不安卻不孤單 對嗎"},{"pid":"6bd03aac36c92a83de65be85f8b27bd2d1b45ed7","tid":1652400,"uid":199050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:20:40.000Z","msg":"之前雨傘集會聽到眼濕濕<br />\n咁就5年啦，唔好忘記我地嘅初衷"},{"pid":"7a1d38a577fd0d94c191d0b5233dca57a9463230","tid":1652400,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:21:00.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑撚死，五毛入侵連登開始帶風向同國難五金割蓆。成班懵撚爭住和應<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"095569cddd479343a435038da14e2d2f2710efd8","tid":1652400,"uid":168381,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:21:19.000Z","msg":"收檔啦，左膠歌，逢聽必輸。"},{"pid":"7733770ff75c9d99a78516847646a5bcbb5a7ecb","tid":1652400,"uid":12169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:22:04.000Z","msg":"謝安琪唔會再唱了"},{"pid":"366f9b5d2ab55fc5e89c6d5ee776657ec4ef5a82","tid":1652400,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾左膠歌"}]}